overview.en: SDS is a decentralized consensus social ecological cycle project, the name of the basic circulation unit within the ecosystem, and the only sharing system and pass-through medium. Its intrinsic financial balance, community promotion, business docking, value precipitation and network expansion will all subvert the notion behind the centralized business model.
overview.zh: SDS是去中心化的共识社会生态循环项目，是生态系统内基本流通单位的名称，是唯一的分享制度与通证传递介质。其内在的金融平衡，社区推广，商业对接，价值沉淀和网络扩张都将颠覆中心化商业模式背后的观念。
